    public class IterableIData
extends WrappedIData
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>>
    Wraps an IData document in an implementation of the Iterable interface, which then allows the use of a standard Java for each loop for iterating over the elements in the document.
